Polling is actively checking something regularly, interrupts pause execution to do a specific thing and then resume

If a process is infrequent, urgent, and asynchronous, interrupts may be better
If a process is frequent, not urgent, and synchronous, polling may be better

Compilation flags:
    -Wall -Wextra -Wpedantic -fanalyzer -Wanalyzer-too-complex -ggdb -Og